---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Boat & RV Guardian | Open-Source Monitoring for Boats & RVs">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-bg-glow"></div>
		<div class="container hero-container">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<span class="hero-eyebrow">Open Source · GPL-3.0 · Free Core App</span>
				<h1 class="hero-title"><span class="text-gradient">Protect</span> your boat or RV — even when you're miles away.</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">
					A free, open-source platform that watches your most critical systems. Dead batteries stop bilge pumps. A burst line on an unlimited city-water hookup can sink a boat or flood a cabin. Guardian catches it early — using affordable, off-the-shelf sensors and automatic shutoff valves.
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions">
					<a href="#downloads" class="btn btn-primary">Get the App — Free</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian" class="btn btn-outline">View on GitHub</a>
				</div>
				<ul class="hero-trust">
					<li>⭐ Open source</li>
					<li>🔒 Local-first &amp; private</li>
					<li>🆓 Free core app</li>
					<li>🛠️ Off-the-shelf hardware</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-image-wrapper">
				<img src="/hero-dashboard.png" alt="Boat & RV Guardian dashboard showing battery, water, and flood status" class="hero-image" />
				<div class="glass-float float-1">
					<div class="float-icon">🔋</div>
					<div>
						<strong>House Battery</strong>
						<span class="status-ok">13.2V · Charging</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="glass-float float-2">
					<div class="float-icon">🚨</div>
					<div>
						<strong>Bilge Sensor</strong>
						<span class="status-ok">Dry</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<span class="image-badge">Illustrative preview</span>
				<span class="hero-image-caption">Illustrative preview — the actual app may look different.</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The Problem -->
	<section class="problem-section container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>What's at stake</h2>
			<p>The failures that ruin a trip — or total a vessel — are almost always quiet ones. They happen while you're asleep, at the office, or three states away.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="problem-grid">
			<div class="glass-card problem-card">
				<div class="problem-icon">🌊</div>
				<h3>City water never sleeps</h3>
				<p>A cracked fitting or burst hose on an unlimited city-water hookup can push <strong>hundreds of gallons</strong> into your cabin or coach while you're away. There's no tank to run dry.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card problem-card">
				<div class="problem-icon">🔋</div>
				<h3>A dead battery is a dead bilge pump</h3>
				<p>Lose your 12V system and you lose the bilge pump, the fridge, and your safety electronics. On the water, a flat house bank can quietly become an emergency.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card problem-card">
				<div class="problem-icon">⚡</div>
				<h3>Shore power drops silently</h3>
				<p>A tripped pedestal at the marina or campground kills your charging and refrigeration — and you won't know until the food spoils or the batteries are flat.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How It Works -->
	<section class="how-it-works">
		<div class="container row-reverse-layout">
			<div class="content-side">
				<span class="hero-eyebrow">How it works</span>
				<h2>Smart-home hardware, built for the water and the road</h2>
				<p>Guardian doesn't sell you proprietary marine electronics at marine prices. It turns the same affordable IoT sensors and valves used in millions of homes — LinkTap and Shelly — into a purpose-built monitoring system for vessels and rigs.</p>
				<ul class="benefit-list">
					<li><strong>Sense:</strong> Flood sensors, voltage monitors, and power meters watch the systems that matter.</li>
					<li><strong>Decide:</strong> The app — on your phone, laptop, or nav station — tracks every reading in real time.</li>
					<li><strong>Act:</strong> When a line bursts, the LinkTap valve slams shut automatically and you get a push notification anywhere in the world.</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/devices" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">See the hardware &amp; costs &rarr;</a>
			</div>
			<div class="image-side">
				<img src="/smart-hardware.png" alt="The off-the-shelf smart hardware Guardian connects to" class="feature-image" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Key Features Grid -->
	<section class="features-section container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>One dashboard for everything</h2>
			<p>Water, power, and climate — monitored locally when you're aboard, and over the cloud when you're not.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="features-grid">
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">🌊</div>
				<h3>Automatic water shutoff</h3>
				<p>LinkTap smart valves meter real-time flow and slam shut the instant usage spikes past your limit — stopping a burst line before it floods.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">🔋</div>
				<h3>12V &amp; shore power health</h3>
				<p>Track house and starter banks plus shore-power status with the Shelly Uni and PM Mini, so a dead battery never strands you.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">📡</div>
				<h3>Instant cloud alerts</h3>
				<p>Shelly sensors fire straight to a Cloudflare Worker, so the push notification reaches you the second water is detected — wherever you are.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">💻</div>
				<h3>Works offline, local-first</h3>
				<p>Aboard and off-grid, the app talks directly to your sensors with zero latency and zero internet. No cloud required to stay protected.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Tailored Protection -->
	<section class="protection-section container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Tailored to how you travel</h2>
			<p>The same system, tuned for the realities of life on the water and on the road.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="protection-grid">
			<div class="glass-card protection-card boat-card">
				<div class="card-icon">⛵</div>
				<h3>For your boat</h3>
				<ul class="protection-list">
					<li>
						<strong>Bilge pump readiness</strong>
						<span>Keep batteries charged so the pump runs when it has to.</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Freshwater burst mitigation</strong>
						<span>Shut the water the moment a freshwater line lets go.</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Power assurance</strong>
						<span>Know your charging is alive before you leave the slip.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="glass-card protection-card rv-card">
				<div class="card-icon">🚐</div>
				<h3>For your RV</h3>
				<ul class="protection-list">
					<li>
						<strong>No dead batteries</strong>
						<span>Catch deep discharge before it kills your bank or starter.</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Burst-pipe defense</strong>
						<span>Limit damage from city-water plumbing failures while you're out.</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Peace of mind</strong>
						<span>Leave the campsite knowing the coach is watching itself.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Open Source Story -->
	<section class="opensource-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="hero-eyebrow">Why it's free</span>
				<h2>Built by boaters and RVers, for boaters and RVers</h2>
				<p>Guardian started with a simple frustration: the gear to protect a vessel or rig was overpriced, locked down, and rented back to you by subscription. So we built the opposite — and gave it away.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card opensource-card">
				<div class="opensource-grid">
					<div class="os-item">
						<h4>💸 Free core, no catch</h4>
						<p>The core app is free and open-source — no license to run it, and you can always self-host. Advanced features may arrive as optional paid add-ons later, but core monitoring and protection stay free.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="os-item">
						<h4>🔓 No vendor lock-in</h4>
						<p>Licensed under GPL-3.0. Read the code, build it yourself, fork it, or run it forever. The project can't be taken away from you.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="os-item">
						<h4>🔒 Your data stays yours</h4>
						<p>Local-first by design. Readings live on your own network unless you explicitly turn on cloud sync for remote alerts.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="os-item">
						<h4>🤝 Community-driven</h4>
						<p>Every fix, sensor, and feature comes from people who actually live this. Open an issue, share a build, or send a pull request.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="opensource-cta">
					<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Star &amp; explore on GitHub</a>
					<a href="/support" class="btn btn-outline">Get involved</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Downloads Section -->
	<section id="downloads" class="downloads-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Get the app</h2>
				<p>Launch the web dashboard instantly, or install a native app for offline control and push notifications.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="downloads-grid">
				<a href="/app/" class="glass-card download-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
					<h3>Web Dashboard</h3>
					<p>Launch the live browser app to configure and monitor your system — nothing to install.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="https://downloads.boatrvguardian.com/boat-rv-guardian_latest.apk" class="glass-card download-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
					<h3>Android APK</h3>
					<p>Sideload the mobile app for on-the-go monitoring and instant push notifications.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="https://downloads.boatrvguardian.com/boat-rv-guardian_latest.dmg" class="glass-card download-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">🍎</div>
					<h3>macOS App</h3>
					<p>Native Apple Silicon and Intel desktop app for your navigation station.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="https://downloads.boatrvguardian.com/boat-rv-guardian_latest.exe" class="glass-card download-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">🪟</div>
					<h3>Windows App</h3>
					<p>Native Windows desktop app optimized for low-power onboard PCs.</p>
				</a>
			</div>
			<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;">
				<p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">
					Looking for older versions?
					<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--accent-color); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 500;">
						View all releases on GitHub &rarr;
					</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="cta-section container">
		<div class="glass-card cta-card">
			<div class="cta-content">
				<h2>Ready to protect your rig?</h2>
				<p>Pick your hardware, install the app, and travel knowing your vessel is watching itself.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="cta-actions">
				<a href="/devices" class="btn btn-primary">See Supported Devices</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian" class="btn btn-outline">View on GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-bg-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: -20%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 800px;
		height: 800px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15) 0%, rgba(11, 15, 25, 0) 70%);
		z-index: -1;
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.hero-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.hero-eyebrow {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1.5px;
		color: var(--accent-color);
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 95%;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hero-trust {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-trust li {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text-main);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.hero-image-wrapper {
		position: relative;
		perspective: 1000px;
	}

	.image-badge {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0.85rem;
		right: 0.85rem;
		z-index: 2;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		color: var(--text-main);
		background: rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.7);
		backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-radius: 6px;
		padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
	}

	.hero-image-caption {
		display: block;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.hero-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		transform: rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(5deg);
		transition: transform 0.5s ease;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.hero-image-wrapper:hover .hero-image {
		transform: rotateY(0) rotateX(0);
	}

	.glass-float {
		position: absolute;
		background: rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.6);
		backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.float-1 { top: 15%; left: -10%; animation-delay: 0s; }
	.float-2 { bottom: 15%; right: -10%; animation-delay: 2s; }
	.float-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }

	.glass-float strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
	}

	.glass-float span { font-size: 0.8rem; }
	.status-alert { color: var(--danger-color); }
	.status-ok { color: var(--success-color); }

	@keyframes float {
		0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
		100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
	}

	/* Section header */
	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.section-header p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	/* Problem Section */
	.problem-section {
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
	}

	.problem-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.problem-card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-top: 3px solid var(--danger-color);
	}

	.problem-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.problem-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.problem-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.problem-card strong { color: #fff; }

	/* How It Works */
	.how-it-works {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.row-reverse-layout {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.content-side h2 {
		font-size: 2.3rem;
		margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
	}

	.content-side p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.benefit-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
	}

	.benefit-list li {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-main);
	}

	.benefit-list li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent-color);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.benefit-list strong { color: #ffffff; }

	.feature-image {
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
	}

	/* Features Section */
	.features-section {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
	}

	.feature-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--surface-color);
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	/* Protection Section */
	.protection-section {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.protection-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.protection-card {
		padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.protection-card::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--accent-gradient);
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.card-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.protection-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.protection-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.protection-list li {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.protection-list li::before {
		content: "🛡️";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0.1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.protection-list strong {
		display: block;
		color: #ffffff;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.protection-list span { color: var(--text-muted); }

	/* Open Source Section */
	.opensource-section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.opensource-card {
		padding: 3rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.06), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.06));
		border-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2);
	}

	.opensource-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.os-item h4 {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.os-item p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.opensource-cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	/* Downloads Section */
	.downloads-section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
	}

	.downloads-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.download-card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		display: block;
	}

	.download-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-color); }

	.download-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.download-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* CTA Section */
	.cta-section { padding: 6rem 2rem; }

	.cta-card {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1));
		border-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
		padding: 4rem;
	}

	.cta-content h2 {
